title: Tech View: Nifty50 forms small bullish candle; further upside possible - Economic Times
content: Tech View: Nifty50 forms small bullish candle; further upside possible  Economic Times
description: Ruchit Jain of 5paisa.com said Nifty50 has retraced 61.8 per cent of the recent corrective phase, which is placed at 17,700-17,800.
